{"tid":26868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔幼園外疑現「拐子佬」家長報警　警：已聯絡校方　未有證據涉拐帶","createTime":"2016-12-07T03:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T07:04:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"777949dbf1a822b8fc23fa5f8ed0e640e488b1c9","tid":26868,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161206/s00001/1481028935022SL4_174BFA42C809799FD43023273D775173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161206%2Fs00001%2F1481028935022SL4_174BFA42C809799FD43023273D775173.jpg&h=2b1d1534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（明報製圖/facebook群祖「Tai Po 大埔」圖片/大埔商會幼稚園網頁圖片）<br />\n<br />\n近日港九均有傳出學校附近疑有「拐子佬」帶走學童，今日網上流傳大埔商會幼稚園的家長通告，指有家長反映近日學校附近出現拐子佬，家長代表已到警署備案，並指警方承諾加派人手巡邏。 <br />\n<br />\n警方回覆本報查詢，指大埔警區人員今日已聯絡該校長及有關家長，會進一步了解事件。警方又稱，非常重視懷疑企圖拐帶兒童的事件，暫時沒有證據顯示，近日事件涉及拐帶兒童。警方將在各區學校附近加強巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的大埔商會幼稚園通告指，最近有家長反映校舍附近出現「行迹可疑的陌生人」，「利用學童的童真和好奇心，接近學童，並有引誘和企圖拐帶的行為」。通告指，校方已於早會通知各班主任，並於上課時教導學童勿接觸陌生人，又提醒家長勿獨留子女於公園玩耍，不要讓子女離開自己視線範圍。<br />\n<br />\n本報傍晚曾致電大埔商會幼稚園查詢事件，接線職員指「不作回應」。<br />\n<br />\n早前九龍塘啟思幼稚園懷疑出現拐子佬拖走學童事件，發通告提醒家長注意。其後香港仔石排灣天主教聖伯多祿幼稚園亦發通告稱，近日南區發現有「陌生人」強抱小朋友個案，提醒家長接送子女時，須看緊及緊拖子女的手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161206/s00001/1481028994551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161206%2Fs00001%2F1481028994551&d=mafjcGSeYPqAN3NPNGcyihpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=149baf9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161206%2Fs00001%2F1481028994551&h=1d21e388\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161206/s00001/1481028994551</a>"},{"pid":"66bdac5dfe97b3a68ae9e5d8a60372a1c0fbe5aa","tid":26868,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通帶佢食雪糕呀"},{"pid":"bf3fe09748d7c5fdf0ab5411c69f3d3c1fe67819","tid":26868,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38abab67afeb29c51d5d8f9997f14fe71e377fd3","tid":26868,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"靠黑警應該死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dc7f39c0d34cf9b5716fae0b333d228ee0badb","tid":26868,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"港豬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46193bab17f0bccfe645a21c2a837b60680ed61","tid":26868,"uid":42452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普遍都靚仔過大陸仔, 應該可以賣多幾百蚊"},{"pid":"867847d9fa4a11f51ff2f5d098f514619533a09f","tid":26868,"uid":51058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"黑警應拉嘅唔拉<br />\n所有效率用哂做政治打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}